Jadi pasti ada video
dia keluar juga, kan?

1136
01:11:44,083 --> 01:11:44,958
Pasti ada.

1137
01:11:45,042 --> 01:11:46,542
Percepat dan periksa!

1138
01:11:48,125 --> 01:11:51,667
Kita sudah menonton penjaga
menggaruk tubuhnya selama 20 menit.

1139
01:11:51,750 --> 01:11:54,250
Telepon aku saat kalian
melihat dia keluar, oke?

1140
01:11:56,708 --> 01:11:57,625
Oke.

1141
01:11:57,708 --> 01:11:58,833
Apa maksudnya "oke"?

1142
01:11:59,917 --> 01:12:01,000
Oke!

1143
01:12:04,458 --> 01:12:05,417
Oke.

1144
